data.description: **NEWLY PAVED STREET, COME SEE! >> 2.25% ASSUMABLE FHA LOAN! TAKE ADVANTAGE OF THE INCREDIBLY LOW INTEREST RATE ON THIS 2020 BUILD! Escape to tranquility on the north shores of Lake Travis! This immaculate 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home offers modern finishes and a quiet lakeside community experience. An added “bonus” room allows flexible options for a 4th bedroom, a hobby room, an exercise room, or a “man-cave!”  Appointed with thoughtful upgrades including wood-plank tile floors, granite countertops, and recessed lighting, you’ll appreciate how “new” this 2020 build feels.  Relax in the master suite's spa-like bathroom, featuring a walk-in closet, dual vanity, a private water closet, and a separate shower and garden tub. Enjoy effortless meals with built-in kitchen appliances, and entertain in the spacious backyard enclosed by a wrought-iron fence and a covered patio. Add on storage for your boat, jet skis, or camper in the oversized side yard, perfect for outdoor enthusiasts! Beyond your doorstep, find endless community amenities: private gated waterfront parks, a golf course, two community pools, two private gyms, a fishing well, hiking trails, disc golf, an events pavilion, private gated playgrounds, picnic areas, marinas, sand volleyball, basketball courts, tennis courts, and more! This is "resort-style" living at its finest - don't miss your chance to experience living the “lake life” in Lago Vista, Texas!  Refrigerator, washer, and dryer included in purchase.
